div.div: Saikyou no Ousama, Nidome no Jinsei wa Nani wo Suru?

After a mysterious death, King Grey is reborn as Arthur Leywin on the magical continent of Dicathen. Although he enters his second life as a baby, his previous wisdom remains. He begins to master magic and forge his own path as the years go by, seeking to correct the mistakes of his past life.
(Source: Crunchyroll)

LycoReco is a caf with a traditional Japanese twist located in downtown Tokyo. But the delicious coffee and sugary sweets are not the only orders this caf takes! From delivering packages short distances, to pick-ups and drop-offs on the lonely streets at night, to zombies and giant monster extermination?! Whatever your problem, we're here to help! We will solve any kind of "trouble" you may have!
Waiting for you are the ever-smiling poster-girl and the cool, serious newcomer. A petite girl who never wants to work and a young woman approaching thirty who wants to get married. And the manager is a nice guy whos obsessed with Japan!
Whatever your order is, leave it all up to us
(Source: Official Site)
Seijo no Maryoku wa Bannou desu

Sei, a 20-year-old office worker, is whisked away to a whole new world. Unfortunately for Sei, the ritual that summoned hermeant to produce a Saint who would banish the dark magicbrought two people over instead of one. And everyone prefers the second girl over Sei?! But this is just fine by Sei, who leaves the royal palace to set up shop making potions and cosmetics with her newfound magic. Business is booming, and this might not be such a bad life, after allas long as her supposed Sainthood doesnt come back to haunt her.
(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)
(Kono Sekai wa Mou Ore ga Sukutte Tomi to Kenryoku wo Te ni Iretashi, Onna Kishi ya Onna Maou to Shiro de Tanoshiku Kurashiteru kara, Ore Igai no Yuusha wa) Mou Isekai ni Konaide Kudasai.

[Question] A new different world hero appeared on Horizon [Answer] Turn back to Earth right now!
After the struggle, I saved the other world and tried to enjoy the rest of my life freely. But for some reason, the incarnating hero from the earth will spring up here on the Horizon. Don't be silly! This world is mine!
The Holy Knight, the Demon Girl, the Elves, the Beastmen, and even the ordinary people, everything in this world will never be given to anyone!
NEET? Izakaya? SDF? No matter who the enemy is! Other-hero, turn back to the Earth!
Drive back all the other world hero with wisdom, courage and perfection, a slapstick fantasy opens!
(Source: Kadokawa, translated)
